            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="37413875">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">在思维里，只有思想才是对象……（思想也可以堕入非理性</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-03-20 16:54</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>在思维里，只有思想才是对象……（思想也可以堕入非理性</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
